node.title: Rescuers unable to save drowning victim at Bethells Beach
node.description: Rescuers were unable to save a person who has drowned at Te Henga Bethells Beach in Auckland this afternoon.
node.content:
["Rescuers were unable to save a person who has drowned at Te Henga Beach in Auckland this afternoon.", "", "
Te Henga beach, on Auckland's west coast. Photo: RNZ / Nick Monro
", "Police were notified of someone in trouble in the water just after 3.30pm, a spokesperson said in a statement.", "The Eagle helicopter and surf lifesavers were scrambled, and rescuers managed to find the person in the water.", "However, police said despite CPR attempts on shore the person died."]
